# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User settings
xcuserdata/

## Xcode 8 and earlier
*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/

## Build results
build/
DerivedData/
.build-dd/
dist/

## Built app bundles (produced locally for testing)
*.app

## Bundled offline Whisper model (large; fetch via scripts/fetch_whisper_model.sh)
WhisperBundle/

## Claude Code local workspace files
.claude/

## Internal product / design docs — our own IP, must NOT be published
产品开发文档-*.md
产品开发文档*.md
*-PRD.md
docs/internal/
## Internal business / strategy notes — our own discussion, must NOT be published
CueFlow-变现与发布计划-总结.md
*-总结.md
*变现*.md

## Marketing landing page — hosted on the web, NOT published to this repo
landing/

## Non-Apple files
.DS_Store

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/

## Other
*.lock
*.mode1v3
*.mode2v3
*.perspectivev3
*.pbxuser
*.xccheckout
*.xcscmblueprint
*~.nib
